t:
skydiving would be fun.
  I paid attention when the instructor
 went over all the safety measures,
everything that can go wrong.



But now I don't know what to do —
it has been two days,
and I'm still falling.
c:
There's no sign of the ground, infact anything.



Good morning. What did you use to think and now you don’t? #Collab & pen it down. #usedtothink #YourQuoteAndMine
Collaborating with YourQuote Baba





#skydiving #safety #void #jump #forever
